<TD><B><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica"><FONT SIZE=+1>Firm Wants to Erect Two
Cell Sites in Indianapolis Area</FONT></FONT></B></TD>

<TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">The Carmel Clay School Board in Indianapolis
is reviewing Cellular One Communications' request to erect two nine-story
communication towers concealed as flagpoles, one at Smoky Row Elementary
School and another at the school corporation's soccer complex. Residents
are expected to oppose the construction. (<A HREF="http://www.wow-com.com/results/professional/news/frameindex.cfm?articleid=3348">WOW-COM</A>)</FONT></TD>

