<TD><B><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica"><FONT SIZE=+1>Ericsson Announces New
Mobile Phone Forecast for 1998-2000</FONT></FONT></B></TD>

<TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">Ericsson expects that the global mobile
