<TD><B><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica"><FONT SIZE=+1>Ericsson Eyes Cell Phone
Market for Teenagers</FONT></FONT></B></TD>

<TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">Ericsson said it is possible it will launch
cell phones aimed at parents wanting to keep in contact with their children.
If such a product were launched, Ericsson said, "it would be marketed responsibly
to adults only, and [Ericsson] would certainly position it as a communication
tool -- not a toy." (<A HREF="http://www.techweb.com/wire/story/TWB19980827S0004">TECHWEB</A>)</FONT></TD>

